{"tid":734910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京傳再驅逐低端人口　工廠老闆：太不人性化","createTime":"2018-07-09T05:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T07:11:16.000Z","uid":75969,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e20ea541e5a51e61e24c2313bb6cbdf38c7e27fe","tid":734910,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180709/photo/bkncn-20180709104258564-0709_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180709104330\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180709%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180709104258564-0709_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180709104330&h=99dc2520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">北京去年底被指清退「低端人口」，多名外來人士被迫搬離。（互聯網）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n北京大興區於2017年11月造成27人傷亡的奪命大火後，當局加強排查並逼走多戶居民，被指趁機驅離「低端人口」。境外媒體報道，當局近日在北京市郊的大興區及順義區等地，再次進行針對外來人口的驅離行動。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，大興區青雲店鎮寺上村區鎮兩級政府於上周四（5日）上午，曾出動逾百人聯合執法，查抄當地3家服裝公司，有不滿的在場民眾被警方逮捕。當地居民表示，服務業對於大興區居民而言，是重要的生產力來源。除了服務廠，大興區內其他工廠早前也接獲通知要求遷離。<br />\n<br />\n另美國媒體記者實地視察後，發現大興區、順義區多個村莊被要求整改，租客限期搬離的通告隨處可見。目前大批從事服務行業的外來人員已離開北京，還有部分小型工廠選擇留下。一名工廠老闆對此無奈表示：「人家需要你的時候，你就是高端人才，不需要你就低端，只能這麽解釋。我感覺北京真是太不人性化了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180709/bkncn-20180709104258564-0709_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180709%2Fbkncn-20180709104258564-0709_05011_001.html&d=EpBiDWHeHEVQSoaZVRr9hRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=9251c553\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180709/bkncn-20180709104258564-0709_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"700dbc432d60321925c3cac0ce4c03d0ef377954","tid":734910,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:21:13.000Z","msg":"竟然係因報，反了、反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b1044559989e277e89234af86b8bf8ad40bde5","tid":734910,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:33:19.000Z","msg":"大陸做緊D野咁似北韓早兩年行條路?"},{"pid":"34495f4cfecf07c62c7c09d8401152f48db9f835","tid":734910,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d外賣淘寶邊個送?"},{"pid":"07e4e4de39f00ed155553c09cb9783f4eb65847e","tid":734910,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"香港都需要清理低端人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135e2fa2bc5066c1af3943864dd5331ba54ad0c9","tid":734910,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:48:55.000Z","msg":"香港跟唔上北京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0f1134816b7335a7cafa17b34282e3fc69ef2c","tid":734910,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"同連登仔方向一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗俾時事台啲人管治香港分分鐘仲死得多人過赤柬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8abb9064563b01b57eb3e0858a271724b010b6e","tid":734910,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:02:54.000Z","msg":"係咪攪緊『剩女下鄉』<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e3352f92172dd421b6c50df35d27e76bc2d0aa","tid":734910,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"07e4e4de39f00ed155553c09cb9783f4eb65847e","tid":734910,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"香港都需要清理低端人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:03:44.000Z","msg":"就快 好似話月頭會清天橋乞兒"},{"pid":"a196be6c0a6448f773509d206d4fa4597